1355
1935
A PENRILLHSS RISH 1OLIGRANT BOY

ENTRLLIGENCE, INTRGRIEY AND INTREPIDITY
TO DE A STURDY ADIRRICAN CITIZERN, A
SALE-HDUCATED
A WHOLE-BARTHD HUMANITARIA, THE
FAXTHBR OF THIES CYTYS WATER SYSTEM
AND THE HULLDAR OF EHE LOS ANICHLES
ADJEDICT:
ENGINAMRING GRNIUS,
THIS MBOIORTAL. IS GRARRULLY
DEDICATBD DY THOSE WHO AREt
AANNON HSIATESNN SIH A0 SLRBlaiaa
AND THE DRNBEICIARIES OF HIS PRORHBTIC
VISION.
